text: Óscar Alfonso del Real Muñoz (born 4 March 1948) is a Mexican politician from the Institutional Revolutionary Party. From 2000 to 2003 he served as Deputy of the LVIII Legislature of the Mexican Congress representing Zacatecas. ==References== Category:1948 births Category:Living people Category:Politicians from Zacatecas Category:Members of the Chamber of Deputies (Mexico) Category:Institutional Revolutionary Party politicians Category:21st-century Mexican politicians
